{"tid":961954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【插胸自殘】九龍塘男保安利刀自插胸口　昏迷送院搶救","createTime":"2018-12-30T13:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T02:41:23.000Z","uid":160807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a5802bf527a59d517a7802766d41502759c82ad6","tid":961954,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2263305/org/420591f2c6250273f33b3e4f037289be.jpg/UFoBF1Z0_E8R6exgTXj0mVJNdAP_sAe6fV9wZH1fcGQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2263305%2Forg%2F420591f2c6250273f33b3e4f037289be.jpg%2FUFoBF1Z0_E8R6exgTXj0mVJNdAP_sAe6fV9wZH1fcGQ&h=ff2093e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男保安利刀自插胸口<br />\n<br />\n周六（29日）凌晨約3時半，警方接獲一名男子報案，指其胞兄於九龍塘又一村海棠路66號，香港基督教女青年會轄下一間會舍，以利刀自插胸口尋死，他血流如注倒地，不省人事。救護員趕抵立即男事主送往瑪嘉烈醫院，當時他陷於昏迷，其後再轉送伊利沙伯醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n胞弟趕至報警　事主昏迷送院<br />\n<br />\n45歲姓何男事主，於上址任職保安員，事發時他WhatsApp其43歲胞弟透露死念，其弟趕抵時已發現他跪於上址地下位置的地面上，毫無反應，身旁遺有約一呎長生果刀。警方翻看閉路電視片段後，發現事主曾用刀自插胸口數下，但並無檢獲遺書，將案件列作「企圖自殺」處理，正追查事件內情。<br />\n<br />\n曾推分娩住宿套餐<br />\n<br />\n今日凌晨，發生自殘案的香港基督教女青年會，樓高六層。大樓服務包括婦女事工隊、家庭健康促進中心、臨床心理服務、紹邦幼兒學校、又一村持續教育中心及女青雅舍。早於2012年，女青雅舍遭傳媒揭發提供分娩住宿套餐，為入住者提供嬰兒床受點餐服務等，其後分娩住宿服務已取消。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/276542/%E6%8F%92%E8%83%B8%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%98-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%A1%98%E7%94%B7%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E5%88%A9%E5%88%80%E8%87%AA%E6%8F%92%E8%83%B8%E5%8F%A3-%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%90%B6%E6%95%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F276542%2F%25E6%258F%2592%25E8%2583%25B8%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%2598-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25A1%2598%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2588%2580%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%258F%2592%25E8%2583%25B8%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2%25E6%2590%25B6%25E6%2595%2591&d=ICFvpbu%2Byt6DMcmIko%2BeW%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=733d5857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/276542/%E6%8F%92%E8%83%B8%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%98-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%A1%98%E7%94%B7%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E5%88%A9%E5%88%80%E8%87%AA%E6%8F%92%E8%83%B8%E5%8F%A3-%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%90%B6%E6%95%91</a>"},{"pid":"d8f2b7feb65cc7d56a581b4652a4815235af0b98","tid":961954,"uid":160807,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:49:36.000Z","msg":"對死亡尊嚴既莊重同執著，值得尊敬同佩服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed08fff710a0d7e4cb018921a315c8dda4dbb9c","tid":961954,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:49:57.000Z","msg":"屈蛇做乜咁傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c503727bcb3beeccd9773187f323104338bf11","tid":961954,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"武士道精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bedf2ce95b1c4c2d30900ab8e69d414fe0c4eb99","tid":961954,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:53:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e6e9009354ee497e35790720001ed4d264484e1","tid":961954,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:53:53.000Z","msg":"攞刀插自己咁撚痛都做得出"},{"pid":"013a28c1cad0f613cd0ca81ded75783a74c28703","tid":961954,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4c503727bcb3beeccd9773187f323104338bf11","tid":961954,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"武士道精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji